{"tid":2350613,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴打 為左令連登所有會員都能夠接受2021叱咤賽果 我決定左出道","createTime":"2021-01-02T12:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T14:09:11.000Z","uid":388757,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1a40bbf7576d134fcf4fe193e30636922e4443","tid":2350613,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"利申22歲 開始甩頭髮<br />\n身高168<br />\n單眼皮 <br />\n農民工膚色<br />\n扁鼻<br />\n一字眉<br />\n哨牙<br />\n成面暗瘡<br />\nA0青頭<br />\n平日衣著打扮key我落金鐘連登仔入面完全無違和感<br />\n住公屋<br />\n讀緊第4年IVE 準備讀poly top up degree<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無鄉音 唱功算係周柏豪級數(連登仔：鏈住春袋老牛聲0唱功）<br />\n<br />\n唔識跳舞（同大家一樣最憎泡狗）<br />\n<br />\n我準備好出道 歌路應該會參考連登仔最鍾意既陳奕迅路線 <br />\n<br />\n政治立場我會選擇最有希臘悲劇色彩既張敬軒路線(平日抽政府水 大是大非受公司滅聲 保護家人護旗）"},{"pid":"58d89932a7439d06f4c2531a841db8563dfa6435","tid":2350613,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb51d0f2772b0c280f363cd38dec5962686585d","tid":2350613,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"on9，你係咪反姜b係咪藍絲嚟㗎"},{"pid":"1b21e7184e4a6c27ed74bb15911827644963df76","tid":2350613,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:46:26.000Z","msg":"樓上真人10碎 早幾日氹老母轉寬頻攞isp開連登acc<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好回 拉到佢陷鄉產"},{"pid":"6604788ccde83c491f40d3dcf1fd1bbb8baca7c0","tid":2350613,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fb51d0f2772b0c280f363cd38dec5962686585d","tid":2350613,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"on9，你係咪反姜b係咪藍絲嚟㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"我有份投左姜濤。<br />\n<br />\n算係有份加害連登仔。<br />\n<br />\n我出道完全係贖罪，捨身取義。"},{"pid":"c55d94b6cb2993d73f2187c78f7938d81addc5db","tid":2350613,"uid":111460,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:47:29.000Z","msg"